Ask HN: Who / is anyone going to jail over SVB catastrophe?
text: SVB collapse looks like a clear case where people made reckless actions that hurt many other people. The people who are responsible are easy to identify so they can be prosecuted. Is this going to happen? Or is SVB management insulated from this?

Ask HN: Why Does Excel Default to Scientific Freaking Notation
text:
When is the last time someone actually wanted Scientific Notation in their Spreadsheet?

Why on earth does Excel default to Scientific Notation for all large numbers?

How many errors can be attributed to Excel converting GTIN's, serial numbers, tracking numbers, event id's and worse into complete gibberish.

Excel Team - What gives!?

title: Tractor-towed Vulcan automatically spots and pulls weeds
Show HN: Dorsia, automatic analytics using Google Sheet
text:
Hello there,

We are the creators of Dorsia, a solution that aims to replace datalayer implementation on the client with an easier, more performant and privacy-wise solution that would allow marketers to leverage tools they already know instead of filing JIRA tickets for tracking additions to the existing client side data layer.

This is still an early beta but we have a live functional demo (read only for now, need to setup authent, stripe, etc..) so feel free to play with it and to let us know what you think :)
